channel.name: Iguana Configuration Manager
channel.description:
This proof of concept working for Iguana on 64 bit linux and 64 bit Windows.
It makes it easier to pull down new 6.0 versions of Iguana and upgrade to them and to rollback if necessary.
This is definitely in ALPHA. You should only run this on a test system and please contact iNTERFACEWARE before you play with this.
